No matter how, remember to dodge all obstacles, and dodge the opposing subway trains. Check out the gorgeous organic environments with tricky temple obstacle, power ups and achievements.

DUCK to avoid being hit. Unlock characters to experience this subway chase in a unique way! Keep chasing them to increase your coin collection to buy super powers for this real chase.Jump over bus and many other vehicles in this rush. Epic landscapes and dynamic action are waiting for you. RACE as fast as possible! Are you ready to adventure across HD worlds and learn different infinite runner’s mechanics?

Challenge your friends to rush and beat your score to be the top player. If you love temple chase games, then this games with varying obstacle like bus, temple arches, water and high hoops are made to make you slip and fall! Guide your superhero to overcome obstacles and avoid enemies. Travel on plains, caverns, ghost houses, airships and castles. Bash them out the way and grab their coins to clear up the streets once and for everyone!

This happy go lucky adventure promises hours of endless run-games to keep you hooked. Change to play as a girl or a surfer or any one of the whacky models created for you. This beautifully detailed world comes to life on mobile and tablet – never has an endless runner looked so good! This game is completely optimised to avoid any lags and to perform effortlessly on a tablet or on a mobile device.

Low size requirements and easy to learn intuitive controls set this apart from the other games to make it loved my millions around the world. Get exhilarating jumping, turning, running, and sliding with captivating game-play and numerous rewards. The path is full of sharp razor like hurdles, skeletons, grumpy rocks and many others. Amazing boost ups, diamonds & jewels will help you survive along. Interactivity of the environment, sound effect and game-play is even interesting to witness.

-One hand playing controls make this very easy to play.
- Fluent screen touch & realistic gravity-jump and fall.

- Easy to use interface
- Cool artwork and cutesy surroundings
- All your friend is playing it - can you beat their high scores?!
